{"tid":913941,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔自相矛盾？［肥絲］","createTime":"2018-11-23T19:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T10:02:08.000Z","uid":179026,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"094339a3e73d509cc30148aeb760cea92e1c1e03","tid":913941,"uid":179026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T19:48:56.000Z","msg":"其實連登仔咁憎人打錯字<br />\n次次見到都屌哂人老母<br />\n打錯字既人好似做左十惡不赦既事咁<br />\n如圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/24/034405_ff144cdb2a0a81f40b188348a9275832.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F24%2F034405_ff144cdb2a0a81f40b188348a9275832.png&h=675bca47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n挽，牙，系，吾，戈 等等呢啲字眼<br />\n都等同擺老母上枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但連登仔同時又好憎肥絲大隻<br />\n明明肥絲就係糾正人既錯別字<br />\n可以稱爲正字邢警<br />\n偏偏好多連登仔都話block 9佢<br />\n<br />\n都唔明你地諗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda220c8c904eaf854cce487b82cb55abda108d7","tid":913941,"uid":31475,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T19:49:57.000Z","msg":"連登仔垃圾囉"},{"pid":"c598ffd9edec813917e8bc6790a3c5a2fda7e6c0","tid":913941,"uid":190333,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T19:51:56.000Z","msg":"不嬲都雙重標準、寬己嚴人架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf2fb359a71d5aea82cfb5fc531def8514ac9a7","tid":913941,"uid":181797,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T19:52:30.000Z","msg":"冇矛盾呀，憎肥絲個班咪係打錯字個班囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35fdeb6959b06d422aaf9e649db84a95693e6c6","tid":913941,"uid":223077,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T19:55:40.000Z","msg":"兒登 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fabbcf5c77430